Class SQLXMLImpl.XMLCopier.SAX.Parsing

java.lang.Object
org.postgresql.pljava.jdbc.SQLXMLImpl.XMLCopier
org.postgresql.pljava.jdbc.SQLXMLImpl.XMLCopier.SAX.Parsing
Enclosing class:
SQLXMLImpl.XMLCopier.SAX
static class SQLXMLImpl.XMLCopier.SAX.Parsing extends SQLXMLImpl.XMLCopier
Copier for a SAXSource that does not supply its own XMLReader.

Such a source needs a parser constructed here, which may, like any parser, require adjustment. Such a source is effectively a stream source snuck in through the SAX API.
